DELETE /expenses/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {token}
```

**Respuesta exitosa — 200:**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Gasto eliminado exitosamente",
    "data": null
}
```

**Errores posibles:**
| Código | Motivo                 |
|--------|------------------------|
